tool_description:
FREE stock market related data updated daily!

- SP 500 | DJIA |  Nasdaq100 | ETF 100 | Dividend Kings | Dividends Aristrocrats AND MORE 

-  EOD market data,
title: Stock Compare

api_list.name: Symbol
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://stock-compare.p.rapidapi.com/symbol/{symbol}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "stock-compare.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
